<li>Utilize a hardware wallet or secure software wallet to store and manage ADA securely.</li>



<li>Regularly update software and applications to ensure they are equipped with the latest security features.</li>



<li>Enable two-factor authentication to add an extra layer of security to your ADA transactions.</li>



