<p>Cardano takes several steps to ensure the privacy of user transactions. These include the use of cryptographic techniques such as zero-knowledge proofs and ring signatures, as well as the integration of privacy-focused protocols like zk-SNARKs and zk-STARKs.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">How Do Privacy Measures in Cardano Impact the Scalability and Performance of the Network?</h3>



