<p>If you suspect your wallet&#8217;s been compromised, immediately transfer assets to a new wallet, update your security protocols, and report the incident to Cardano&#8217;s support team for a thorough investigation and guidance.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">How Does Cardano&#8217;s Security Framework Adapt to Emerging Quantum-Computing Threats That Could Potentially Break Current Encryption Methods?</h3>



<p>You&#8217;ll benefit from Cardano&#8217;s proactive adaptation to quantum threats, as they&#8217;re researching quantum-resistant algorithms to replace vulnerable encryption before such computing power becomes widely accessible, ensuring your assets remain secure.</p>



